Beneath the heavens, dark and vast,
With dreams and shadows that we cast;
The universe calls me to play,
In its whispers, I long to stay.

Through the stars, my spirit flies,
In the wonder of the skies;
Here in nature, I am whole,
Finding freedom for my soul.

- Andrew Lang
